column2: Aap Ko Dekhkar Dekhta Rah Gaya
Apne Hathon Ki Lakeeron Mein Basale Mujhko
Baat Niklegi To Phir Door Talak(Nazm)
Dost Ban Ban Ke Mile Mujhko Mitane Wale
Sarakti Jaye Hai Rukh Se Naqab Aahista Aahista
Tere Khushboo Mein Base Khat-Jagjit Singh
Aaj Ke Daur Mein Ae Dost Ye Manjhar
Ab Aksar Chup Chup Se Rahe Hain
Ab Khushi Hai Na Koi Dard Rulanewala
Ab Main Rashan Ki Qataron Mein Nazar Aata Hoon
Ab Mere Paas Tum Aayee Ho
Ab To Ghabrake Yeh Kahte Hain
Agar Hum Kahen Aur Woh Muskura Den
Aise Hijr Ke Mausam Ab Kab Aate Hain
Ajab Apna Haal Hota Jo Visaal
Aye Khuda Ret Ke Sehra Ko Samandar Karde
Bahot Pahle Se Un Qadmon Ki Aahat Jaan Lete Hain
Bahut Pahele Se Un Kadmo Ki Aahat Jaan Lete Hain
Chand Ke Saath Kai Dard Purane Nikle
Dard Badhkar Fugan Na Ho Jaye
Darwaza Khula Rakhna-Rahon Pe Nazar Rakhna
Dekha Jo Aaina To Mujhe Sochna Pada
Dhai Din Na Jawani Nal Chaldi
Dhoop Hai Kya Aur Saya Hai
Dhoop Main Niklo Ghataon Mein Nakakar Dekho
Dil Ko Gham-E-Hayat Gawara Hai In Dinon
Dil Ko Kya Ho Gaya Khuda Jane
Ek Na Ek Shama Andhere Mein Jalaye Rakhiye
Ek Nazar Dekh Ke Hum Jaan Gaye
Gham Badhe Aate Hain Qatil Ki Nigahon Ki Tarah
Har Ore Tabhai Ka Manzar (With Narration)
Huzoor Aapka Bhi Ehtram Karta Chaloon
Jab Kabhi Tere Naam Lete Hain
Jab Se Hum Tabha Ho Gaye
Jawan Hai Raat Saqiya Sharaab La Sharaab La
Jawani Ke Heele Haya Ke Bahane
Kabhi Yun Bhi Aa Meri Aankh Mein
Kisi Ranjish Ko Hawa Do Ke Main Zinda Hoon Abhi
Kya Sach Hai Kya Jhoot Hai
Main Khayal Hoon Kisi Aur Ka
Manzil Na De Charagh Na De
Maye Ni Main Ik Shikra Yaar Banaya
Mera Dil Bhi Shauq Se Todo
Mil Kar Juda Hue To Na Soya Karenge Haam
Na Shivale Na Kalisa Na Haram Jhoothe Hain
Na Tha Kuchh To Khuda Tha
Pahle To Apne Dil Ki Raza Jaan Jaiye
Pareshan Raat Sari Hai Sitaron Tum To So Jao
Pathar Ke Khuda Pathar Ke Sanam
Phir Kuchh Is Dil Ko Beqarari Hai
Raat Bhi Neend Bhi Kahani Bhi
Sadma To Hai Mujhe Bhi Ki Tujhse Juda Hoon Main
Suna Tha Ki Woh Aayenge Anjuman-Live
Sunte Hai Ki Mil Jaati Hai (Live)
Tum Nahin Gham Nahin Sharab Nahin
Tumhari Anjuman Se Uth Ke Deewane Kahan Jate
Tumne Sooli Pe Latakte Jise Dekha Hoga
Uske Hothon Pe Kuchh Kapta Rah Gaya
Uski Hasrat Hai Jise Dil Se Mita
Woh Firaaq Aur Woh Visal Kahan
Woh Rulakar Hans Naa Paya Der Tak
Yeh Bhi Kya Ehsaan Kam Hai
Yeh Mojiza Bhi Mohabbat Kabhi Dikhaye Mujhe
Yeh To Nahin Ke Gham Nahin
Zindagi Se Badi Saza Hi Nahin
Zindegi Se Badi Saza Hi Nahin
Tu Nahin To Zindagi Mein Aur Kya
Mere Dil Mein Tu Hi Tu Hai
Tum Itna Jo Muskura Rahe Ho
Tum Ko Dekha To Yeh Khayal Aaya
Yeh Tera Ghar Yeh Mera Ghar
Gham Ka Khazana Tera Bhi Hai Mera Bhi
Har Taraf Har Jagah Besumar Aadmi
Mili Hawaon Mein Udne Ki Woh Saza
